OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDesmond Tutu's daughter    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbarred from leading funeral
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The late Desmond Tutu's daughter has   
OL,6, been barred by the Church of England   
OL,7, from leading a funeral because she is  
OL,8, married to a woman.                    
OL,10,FMpho Tutu van Furth is an Anglican     
OL,11,Fpriest in the Diocese of Washington and
OL,12,Fhad been asked to officiate at the     
OL,13,Ffuneral of her late-godfather, Martin  
OL,14,FKenyon, in Shropshire on Thursday.     
OL,16,FMs Tutu van Furth told BBC News it     
OL,17,F"seemed really churlish and hurtful".  
OL,19,FThe Diocese of Hereford said it was "a 
OL,20,Fdifficult situation".                  
